For example,

246
00:17:21,120 --> 00:17:24,350
it looks like you have an ill omen, Madam.

247
00:17:25,180 --> 00:17:27,230
So ominous!

248
00:17:27,230 --> 00:17:30,590
- Where did you scammers come from? Quickly leave!
- What are you doing?

249
00:17:30,590 --> 00:17:33,830
If My Lady says you have an ill omen, then you do.

250
00:17:37,450 --> 00:17:42,020
Madam, your complexion is dull, glabella is dark, and footsteps are unsteady.

251
00:17:42,020 --> 00:17:44,620
I am guessing that you cannot sleep soundly at night.

252
00:17:44,620 --> 00:17:47,300
If this continues, your body will not be able to endure it.

253
00:17:47,300 --> 00:17:49,100
You're spewing nonsense!

254
00:17:49,100 --> 00:17:52,850
Let me tell you. I-I'm warning you out of the kindness of my heart.

255
00:17:52,850 --> 00:17:58,540
If you want to treat illnesses and save people, then you should go to the countryside, where there are hardly any physicians and medicines.

256
00:17:58,540 --> 00:18:02,090
Don't be here, playing tricks.

257
00:18:02,090 --> 00:18:04,240
You are just saying things to gain attention!

258
00:18:04,240 --> 00:18:06,970
- Let's go, let's go. Hurry.
- Let's go, let's go.

259
00:18:08,030 --> 00:18:11,010
Y-You go get someone to clean this area.

260
00:18:11,010 --> 00:18:14,040
- Don't just let anyone come in.
- Yes.

261
00:18:15,260 --> 00:18:17,550
- Madam, be careful.
- So strange.

262
00:18:19,090 --> 00:18:20,980
[Zhou Residence]

263
00:18:22,380 --> 00:18:25,590
- Liu'er, let's go.
- All right.

264
00:18:28,750 --> 00:18:35,050
You don't say, Miss Jun is really patient and tolerant.

265
00:18:35,830 --> 00:18:39,550
Shopkeeper Liu, d-do we keep following them?

266
00:18:39,550 --> 00:18:41,960
No. Let's go back to Jiuling Hall.

267
00:18:41,960 --> 00:18:44,050
When she is back for lunch,

268
00:18:44,050 --> 00:18:47,070
I have some things I need to ask her face to face.

269
00:18:48,700 --> 00:18:51,950
[Jiuling Hall]

270
00:18:51,950 --> 00:18:54,440
Let me hold it.

271
00:18:54,440 --> 00:18:56,500
Be careful.

272
00:19:02,330 --> 00:19:03,770
- Miss Jun, you're back.
- Shopkeeper Liu.

273
00:19:03,770 --> 00:19:04,860
We're back.

274
00:19:04,860 --> 00:19:06,210
Shopkeeper Liu.

275
00:19:08,030 --> 00:19:09,510
There are some things

276
00:19:09,510 --> 00:19:12,350
I-I want to discuss with you.

277
00:19:12,350 --> 00:19:14,980
Sure, go ahead.

278
00:19:14,980 --> 00:19:19,270
Miss Jun, you're a physician.

279
00:19:19,270 --> 00:19:23,220
Don't tell people they have ill omens the moment you see them.

280
00:19:23,220 --> 00:19:25,520
That's inappropriate.

281
00:19:26,270 --> 00:19:28,180
You know about it?

282
00:19:29,920 --> 00:19:34,660
Miss Jun, forgive me for being straightforward.

283
00:19:36,050 --> 00:19:41,660
A-Are you planning on scamming or pretending?

284
00:19:41,660 --> 00:19:45,150
- Shopkeeper Liu, how can you call this a scam?
- Liu'er.

285
00:19:45,150 --> 00:19:49,770
If this isn't a scam, what is it? Even supernatural things such as good or bad fortune have been brought up.

286
00:19:49,770 --> 00:19:51,840
Heart bears ghosts, mind bears gods.
 (T/N: meaning that supernatural phenomena come from people's feelings and thoughts)

287
00:19:51,840 --> 00:19:54,460
Illness disturbs the mind and having a weakened vitality lets evil spirits enter easily.

288
00:19:54,460 --> 00:19:57,950
In Madam Zhou's case, her body is weak and her three energies are depleted,
(T/N: essence, qi, and spirit of Traditional Chinese Medicine)

289
00:19:57,950 --> 00:20:00,930
thus she is easily absent-minded.

290
00:20:00,930 --> 00:20:05,080
You mean to say Madam Zhou really is sick?

291
00:20:05,080 --> 00:20:06,890
Yes.

292
00:20:10,240 --> 00:20:12,830
Even if that's the case,

293
00:20:12,830 --> 00:20:16,630
just directly tell her she is sick the next time you see her.

294
00:20:16,630 --> 00:20:18,970
Don't mention an ill omen again.

295
00:20:18,970 --> 00:20:21,010
Illness harms life.

296
00:20:21,010 --> 00:20:23,260
It is an ill omen.

297
00:20:25,620 --> 00:20:27,120
Let's go.

298
00:20:32,780 --> 00:20:35,250
[Ning Residence]

299
00:20:45,000 --> 00:20:50,100
Those who need to see a wandering physician will naturally trust you.

300
00:20:53,600 --> 00:20:56,300
Xiao Ding, will Miss Jun go to the western part of the city today?

301
00:20:56,300 --> 00:21:00,200
She should be. She didn't finish walking around the western part of the city yesterday.

302
00:21:01,200 --> 00:21:05,000
I remember that Eleventh Brother's cousin's wet nurse's son lives in the western part of town.

303
00:21:05,000 --> 00:21:07,700
Tell him to have Miss Jun take a look at him.

304
00:21:08,400 --> 00:21:12,000
Do I tell him that's what you want?

305
00:21:13,000 --> 00:21:14,400
No.

306
00:21:14,400 --> 00:21:18,600
Find him to drink and chat with. Tell him about what happened in Ru'nan.

307
00:21:19,400 --> 00:21:21,000
Young Master, you are so smart.

308
00:21:21,000 --> 00:21:23,000
This way he wouldn't suspect anything.

309
00:21:23,000 --> 00:21:26,200
In addition, Miss Jun will not suspect a thing either.

310
00:21:26,200 --> 00:21:29,700
Young Master, you treat Miss Jun so well.

311
00:21:29,700 --> 00:21:31,400
That's because she herself is great.

312
00:21:31,400 --> 00:21:34,500
If she did not have her medical skills, then I would not do this.

313
00:21:34,500 --> 00:21:39,000
Will you do the same if others had the same skills?

314
00:21:40,200 --> 00:21:42,600
Hurry and go. Don't delay matters.

315
00:21:48,180 --> 00:21:51,920
Others are not her so, naturally, I would not.

316
00:21:53,200 --> 00:21:56,800
Jiuling Hall! Miraculous Physician Jiuling!

317
00:21:56,800 --> 00:21:58,800
Bring one back to life! Curing illnesses!

318
00:21:58,800 --> 00:22:01,600
Older Sister, I want candy! I want candy!

319
00:22:01,600 --> 00:22:04,000
We did not bring candied fruits today.

320
00:22:04,000 --> 00:22:06,200
- We will bring them for you tomorrow.
- Just give me one.

321
00:22:06,200 --> 00:22:08,200
We will bring some for you all next time.

322
00:22:08,200 --> 00:22:10,400
Miss, are you Miss Jun?

323
00:22:10,400 --> 00:22:12,200
Yes, I am.

324
00:22:12,200 --> 00:22:15,600
You are so young. Are you the daughter of Miraculous Physician Jun?

325
00:22:15,600 --> 00:22:17,700
I guess I didn't drink the wine in vain.

326
00:22:17,700 --> 00:22:20,000
I have fulfilled what Young Master asked me to do.

327
00:22:20,000 --> 00:22:23,000
Miss, she seems to know the late master.

328
00:22:23,000 --> 00:22:24,100
That's right.

329
00:22:24,100 --> 00:22:27,200
I know. Your Jun family is very well-known.

330
00:22:27,200 --> 00:22:28,800
Here. Help me see

331
00:22:28,800 --> 00:22:32,000
if my health is all right.

332
00:22:32,000 --> 00:22:33,200
All right.

333
00:22:50,000 --> 00:22:52,000
Madam, you are in good health.

334
00:22:52,000 --> 00:22:53,500
That's impossible.

335
00:22:53,500 --> 00:22:56,200
Check again to see whether I have an ill omen.

336
00:22:56,200 --> 00:22:58,100
Do I need to take any medicine?

337
00:22:58,900 --> 00:23:02,800
Madam, I have felt your pulse. You are very healthy.

338
00:23:02,800 --> 00:23:05,700
You have no ill omen. There is no need for me to do anything.

339
00:23:08,200 --> 00:23:10,600
How can you... How can you be like this?

340
00:23:10,600 --> 00:23:12,600
What kind of physician are you? What kind of miraculous physician are you?

341
00:23:12,600 --> 00:23:16,000
If you are unwilling to see patients, why do you call yourself a miraculous physician?

342
00:23:16,000 --> 00:23:18,600
What kind of person is she? Why is she even a physician?

343
00:23:18,600 --> 00:23:21,000
Let's go. Ignore her.

344
00:23:21,000 --> 00:23:25,100
"Grandmother, you have no ill omen."

345
00:23:25,100 --> 00:23:27,400
"There's no need for me to do anything."

346
00:23:28,200 --> 00:23:30,600
Madam Wang Cao yelled at her in the streets for a long time.

347
00:23:30,600 --> 00:23:34,600
Young Master, you know how Madam Wang Cao is.

348
00:23:34,600 --> 00:23:38,800
She will remember this grudge for the rest of her life. Now the entire capital knows

349
00:23:38,800 --> 00:23:42,700
Miss Jun is a physician who has no conscience and only wants to scam people of their money.

350
00:23:42,700 --> 00:23:44,200
Soon enough...

351
00:23:44,200 --> 00:23:47,800
Jiuling Hall will not be able to stay in business.

352
00:23:52,800 --> 00:23:56,600
Young Master, I did not do as you asked properly.

353
00:23:58,500 --> 00:24:02,400
It's not your fault. It's mine.

354
00:24:02,400 --> 00:24:05,200
What should we do now?

355
00:24:13,200 --> 00:24:15,400
She has always been a strange girl.

356
00:24:16,590 --> 00:24:19,220
She might be plotting something.

357
00:24:20,160 --> 00:24:24,190
I think it best not to interfere with her. Let's just quietly observe.

358
00:24:26,000 --> 00:24:27,400
What did she say?

359
00:24:27,400 --> 00:24:29,800
"You have no ill omen."

360
00:24:29,800 --> 00:24:31,900
"There's no need for me to do anything."

361
00:24:31,900 --> 00:24:33,200
Did she really say that?

362
00:24:33,200 --> 00:24:34,200
Verbatim.

363
00:24:34,200 --> 00:24:36,860
Second Brother, you may not know.

364
00:24:36,860 --> 00:24:38,800
In just a brief period of time,

365
00:24:38,800 --> 00:24:41,600
it has spread throughout the capital so that everyone knows.

366
00:24:41,600 --> 00:24:42,800
No one is unaware.

367
00:24:42,800 --> 00:24:45,200
She really is unpredictable.

368
00:24:45,200 --> 00:24:49,800
Truly. I think this Miss Jun is truly a strange person.

369
00:24:49,800 --> 00:24:51,600
Actually—

370
00:24:51,600 --> 00:24:53,600
Second Brother, my shoulder is suddenly hurting.

371
00:24:53,600 --> 00:24:56,350
Say, should we have Miss June look at it?

372
00:24:56,350 --> 00:24:58,800
Let's see if she'll take a look at me and see if I have an ill omen.

373
00:24:58,800 --> 00:25:01,000
That is easy. I will treat it for you.

374
00:25:01,800 --> 00:25:03,400
It is suddenly fine now.

375
00:25:04,800 --> 00:25:06,600
There is actually a purpose to what she did.

376
00:25:06,600 --> 00:25:08,000
What is it?

377
00:25:08,000 --> 00:25:09,200
Doesn't everyone in the capital

378
00:25:09,200 --> 00:25:12,400
know of Jiuling Hall this way? Although it's mostly criticism,

379
00:25:12,400 --> 00:25:15,000
it's better than no one knowing of it. Right?

380
00:25:16,600 --> 00:25:18,300
I understand now.

381
00:25:18,300 --> 00:25:20,000
She wants to get famous this way.

382
00:25:20,000 --> 00:25:22,400
Then, as long as she finds a difficult illness

383
00:25:22,400 --> 00:25:25,130
and cures it, people will forget the bad reputation.

384
00:25:25,130 --> 00:25:27,600
They'll even praise her, saying she can bring one back to life.

385
00:25:27,600 --> 00:25:29,200
- Second Brother.
- That's a genius strategy.

386
00:25:29,200 --> 00:25:31,000
You really know

387
00:25:31,000 --> 00:25:34,400
this Miss Jun very well.

388
00:25:34,400 --> 00:25:36,700
She did the same thing in Ru'nan.

389
00:25:37,600 --> 00:25:41,000
It's just that this strategy is a bit novel.

390
00:25:41,000 --> 00:25:43,300
She might be attracting too much attention for her own good.

391
00:25:48,000 --> 00:25:51,800
Enough about her. What are we going to eat?

392
00:25:51,800 --> 00:25:55,600
I think that the grilled meat place we went to last time was not bad.

393
00:25:58,800 --> 00:26:02,200
No. What if we run into a drunkard again?

394
00:26:02,200 --> 00:26:04,900
Isn't that exactly what you want?

395
00:26:13,000 --> 00:26:15,800
Madam, here's soup to calm the nerves.

396
00:26:19,600 --> 00:26:24,400
Madam, are you tired? Why don't you go and rest now?

397
00:26:24,400 --> 00:26:27,000
I'm not tired yet. I'll go to sleep later.

398
00:26:27,000 --> 00:26:31,000
Then let me tell you something funny. It is very interesting.

399
00:26:31,000 --> 00:26:34,000
Everyone on the streets is talking about it.

400
00:26:35,000 --> 00:26:36,300
What is it?

401
00:26:36,300 --> 00:26:40,300
That Miss Jun, who always wanders the streets,

402
00:26:40,300 --> 00:26:43,400
got into some trouble today.

403
00:26:43,400 --> 00:26:46,800
Usually, no one finds her to get looked at and that is fine.

404
00:26:46,800 --> 00:26:49,000
Madam Wang Cao who lives on the Huaihua Alley

405
00:26:49,000 --> 00:26:51,300
went to her to be seen.

406
00:26:51,300 --> 00:26:54,400
Yet she said that Madam Wang Cao has no ill omen.

407
00:26:54,400 --> 00:26:56,400
There's no need for her to do anything.

408
00:26:56,400 --> 00:26:59,000
Everyone was laughing about it.

409
00:27:00,000 --> 00:27:01,800
Nanny, what are you talking about?

410
00:27:01,800 --> 00:27:03,400
You can leave now.

411
00:27:17,600 --> 00:27:20,400
Did you tell anyone about what Miss Jun

412
00:27:20,400 --> 00:27:22,800
said to me a few days ago?

413
00:27:26,400 --> 00:27:30,600
Although it is said that all people are created equal,

414
00:27:30,600 --> 00:27:33,000
Buddha only helps those who help themselves.

415
00:27:33,800 --> 00:27:36,300
A couple of days ago, she stopped me of all people

416
00:27:36,300 --> 00:27:39,200
and said those words about an ill omen.

417
00:27:40,370 --> 00:27:44,920
Could it be that she really saw something?

418
00:28:01,720 --> 00:28:04,410
Madam, what are you looking for?

419
00:28:05,810 --> 00:28:08,170
There's a child crying.

420
00:28:09,200 --> 00:28:11,100
It keeps crying.

421
00:28:15,500 --> 00:28:17,200
Can't you hear it?

422
00:28:18,300 --> 00:28:20,700
I don't hear anything.

423
00:28:21,400 --> 00:28:23,000
Over there.

424
00:28:24,160 --> 00:28:25,710
There.

425
00:28:27,200 --> 00:28:28,600
There.

426
00:28:30,400 --> 00:28:32,000
Go.

427
00:28:32,000 --> 00:28:35,800
Hurry. Hurry and get that physician here. Hurry and go!

428
00:28:35,800 --> 00:28:37,200
Yes.

429
00:28:47,600 --> 00:28:48,700
No.

430
00:28:49,700 --> 00:28:51,800
No, no, no.

431
00:28:53,200 --> 00:28:56,500
No, no, it can't be.

432
00:28:56,500 --> 00:28:58,600
[Jiuling Hall]

433
00:29:00,600 --> 00:29:02,000
Is Physician Jun here?

434
00:29:02,000 --> 00:29:04,200
- Physician Jun!
- Coming!

435
00:29:06,400 --> 00:29:08,000
It's so late. What is it?

436
00:29:08,000 --> 00:29:11,600
I'm from Lord Zhou's residence, Jing Zhaoyin's servant. I am here to ask Miss Jun to make a trip.

437
00:29:11,600 --> 00:29:15,300
- All right, wait a moment. I will go get her.
- All right.

438
00:29:15,300 --> 00:29:16,700
Miss!

439
00:29:39,600 --> 00:29:42,400
Madam, I will write you a prescription.

440
00:29:42,400 --> 00:29:46,400
You will fully recover after following my instructions for half a month.

441
00:29:46,400 --> 00:29:48,100
Half a month?

442
00:29:48,950 --> 00:29:51,590
I've been ill for years now.

443
00:29:51,600 --> 00:29:55,200
I've seen the Imperial Physicians but nothing has changed.

444
00:29:55,200 --> 00:29:58,800
Half a month? How could I recover in half a month?

445
00:30:01,540 --> 00:30:04,500
Illness of the heart (mind) must be treated with medicine for the heart, Madam.

446
00:30:06,000 --> 00:30:08,700
Since I see your ill omen, then I can resolve it.

447
00:30:08,700 --> 00:30:10,600
Trust me.

448
00:30:13,000 --> 00:30:15,220
May I dare ask...

449
00:30:16,020 --> 00:30:18,000
do you have any children?

450
00:30:32,800 --> 00:30:35,900
Back then, I really had no choice.

451
00:30:37,990 --> 00:30:40,800
My husband was observing mourning for his parents.

452
00:30:40,800 --> 00:30:43,400
If I gave birth to the child,

453
00:30:43,400 --> 00:30:46,300
then my husband's future would have been ruined.

454
00:30:46,300 --> 00:30:50,200
Help me tell him (the baby), it's not that I didn't want him.

455
00:30:50,200 --> 00:30:54,600
I really... really had no choice.

456
00:30:56,400 --> 00:31:00,600
Madam, he just came to see you because he is reminiscing about his relationship with you.

457
00:31:00,600 --> 00:31:01,700
No.

458
00:31:02,400 --> 00:31:04,080
Please send him away.

459
00:31:04,080 --> 00:31:06,400
I beg you, Physician Jun.

460
00:31:06,400 --> 00:31:08,800
- Madam, please stand up.
- Please, I'm begging you.

461
00:31:08,800 --> 00:31:10,500
Madam, please stand up.

462
00:31:10,500 --> 00:31:12,200
Please have a seat.

463
00:31:17,800 --> 00:31:19,300
Liu'er.

464
00:31:25,400 --> 00:31:27,600
Give these pills coupled with the calming incense

465
00:31:27,600 --> 00:31:29,900
to Madam daily for half a month.

466
00:31:30,800 --> 00:31:35,600
Miss Jun, is that all that needs to be done?

467
00:31:36,800 --> 00:31:40,500
As long as you sleep well, you will be cured.

468
00:31:52,600 --> 00:31:56,200
Miss, how did you know about the child?

469
00:31:57,000 --> 00:31:59,300
Can you really see things people don't?

470
00:32:01,800 --> 00:32:03,200
Of course not.

471
00:32:03,200 --> 00:32:05,400
I just observed, listened, questioned, and felt her pulse.
 (T/N: four methods of diagnosis)

472
00:32:05,400 --> 00:32:09,000
In addition, there was the doll that never left her side.

473
00:32:09,000 --> 00:32:11,400
Thus, I deduced what happened.

474
00:32:14,000 --> 00:32:16,000
I see.

475
00:32:25,400 --> 00:32:29,000
[Jiuling Hall]

476
00:32:32,000 --> 00:32:35,400
Miss Jun, congratulations on receiving your first consultation fee.

477
00:32:35,400 --> 00:32:39,000
I have heard about what happened yesterday.

478
00:32:39,000 --> 00:32:41,000
Shopkeeper Liu, your congratulations has come too early.

479
00:32:41,000 --> 00:32:44,200
I have not yet collected the consultation fee from yesterday.

480
00:32:45,400 --> 00:32:48,600
You have not yet collected it? What is going on?

481
00:32:48,600 --> 00:32:51,800
Physician Jun, this is the consultation fee as promised.

482
00:32:51,800 --> 00:32:53,200
Here, give it to me.

483
00:32:53,200 --> 00:32:55,700
Please give my thanks to Madam.

484
00:32:55,700 --> 00:32:58,300
Exactly five thousand taels.

485
00:33:00,800 --> 00:33:02,700
Five thousand taels?

486
00:33:03,700 --> 00:33:05,100
Miss Jun,

487
00:33:05,800 --> 00:33:09,600
that much for a consultation fee?

488
00:33:09,600 --> 00:33:10,600
That's right.

489
00:33:10,600 --> 00:33:13,800
Not just anyone or any illness can be looked at by our young miss.

490
00:33:13,800 --> 00:33:16,420
First, we must see if the illness is worth being treated by my young miss.

491
00:33:16,420 --> 00:33:18,600
Then, it is the consultation fee.

492
00:33:18,600 --> 00:33:22,000
Moving forward, our Jiuling Hall can rise to fame.

493
00:33:22,000 --> 00:33:24,900
Miss, will we wander the streets again today?

494
00:33:24,900 --> 00:33:26,200
Yes.

495
00:33:27,600 --> 00:33:31,600
People from the Yunxiao Pavilion said that Lord Huang doesn't go anywhere other than to the imperial court.

496
00:33:31,600 --> 00:33:33,600
- How about Huang Ziqing?
- Same as always.

497
00:33:33,600 --> 00:33:35,100
Leveraging on his father's power,

498
00:33:35,100 --> 00:33:36,970
he is selling government positions for money and bullying commoners.

499
00:33:36,970 --> 00:33:38,600
He is doing everything except humane acts.

500
00:33:38,600 --> 00:33:42,600
Someone needs to teach him a lesson. If I run into him one day...

501
00:33:42,600 --> 00:33:46,700
Second Brother, do you want to see "you have no ill omen

502
00:33:46,700 --> 00:33:48,900
and there's no need for me to do anything"?

503
00:33:52,340 --> 00:33:54,040
No.

504
00:33:54,760 --> 00:33:57,400
So beautiful. There are also these colors.

505
00:33:57,400 --> 00:34:00,800
Jiuling Hall! Miraculous Physician Jiuling!

506
00:34:00,800 --> 00:34:03,200
Specialized in treating various, mysterious and difficult illnesses...

507
00:34:03,200 --> 00:34:07,100
Miss, come and have a look here. Have a look.

508
00:34:12,400 --> 00:34:14,200
Young Lord?

509
00:34:16,000 --> 00:34:17,400
What a coincidence.

510
00:34:17,400 --> 00:34:20,000
That's right. What a coincidence, Miss Jun.

511
00:34:20,000 --> 00:34:24,200
There's no good food, wine, or entertainment here, so you all are...

512
00:34:24,200 --> 00:34:26,640
In your eyes, do I only know how to eat, drink, and play?

513
00:34:26,640 --> 00:34:28,700
Do I never do anything serious?

514
00:34:30,100 --> 00:34:32,300
Young Lord, you have been easily angered recently.

515
00:34:32,300 --> 00:34:35,000
Liu'er, get the Young Lord some medicine.

516
00:34:35,000 --> 00:34:38,800
No need. Baotang's shoulder is injured. Take a look at him.

517
00:34:40,000 --> 00:34:42,800
My shoulder is fine now. There is no need to trouble Physician Jun.

518
00:34:42,800 --> 00:34:45,100
Miss Jun, how about you take a look at me?

519
00:34:45,100 --> 00:34:46,600
Do I have any illness?

520
00:34:46,600 --> 00:34:49,400
No, do I have any ill omen?

521
00:34:55,800 --> 00:34:57,800
Sure.

522
00:35:02,500 --> 00:35:05,800
Take note of how you appear publicly. That's enough.

523
00:35:05,800 --> 00:35:08,800
Young Master, you are very healthy. There is nothing to be worried about.

524
00:35:08,800 --> 00:35:13,000
Miss Jun, are you teasing me?

525
00:35:17,500 --> 00:35:20,300
Sanbing, who knew you would be in this predicament one day too.

526
00:35:24,000 --> 00:35:27,000
Turns out this is how it feels to be teased.

527
00:35:29,500 --> 00:35:32,400
Why did you say "too"?

528
00:35:34,400 --> 00:35:36,200
I understand now.

529
00:35:36,200 --> 00:35:39,800
