540
00:36:13,000 --> 00:36:17,200
I also wonder who it was that snuck into our lady's courtyard every other day.

541
00:36:17,200 --> 00:36:19,800
He even scaled the wall to do it.

542
00:36:21,150 --> 00:36:24,220
You may know a person's exterior but not his heart.

543
00:36:27,410 --> 00:36:29,580
Say, isn't that person thick-skinned?

544
00:36:31,000 --> 00:36:34,300
